{"tid":2203263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又一間IG Shop賣假嘢: mixstudio_clothes","createTime":"2020-09-15T08:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T10:00:29.000Z","uid":82631,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce4f8488844f2cbdccd7bc5b2741c8f7f030b2bb","tid":2203263,"uid":82631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:20:10.000Z","msg":"今日無端端有間賣韓國男裝嘅IG shop走嚟follow我 <br />\n咁小弟就都叫有留意開啲韓國男裝 就㩒入去睇下啦 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gCZWrLF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgCZWrLF.jpg&h=1ec87842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見佢啲圖全部都喺喺人哋啲shop度cap落嚟 我都覺得有啲唔對路㗎啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oc3DE5P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOc3DE5P.jpg&h=bd9f7569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事關我見到有幾張圖有陣支那味 於是決定DM佢問個究竟啦<br />\n<br />\n咁我就是但搵咗一件product問佢攞close up嘅圖啦 想睇下啲料會唔會好差<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9Mqj8J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9Mqj8J.jpg&h=b86e0363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAW54yo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAW54yo.jpg&h=07850ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢一send過嚟就出事啦 我一眼就認出個sup9淘寶牌子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dBVKAFm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdBVKAFm.jpg&h=ac2f5234&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我即刻就問佢係咪淘寶啦 跟住佢就block咗我<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPEWrNr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPEWrNr.jpg&h=0c4035c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nso9sad 仲諗住可能喺我認錯 <br />\n不過既然佢都唔打算解釋咁我就直接放上嚟俾大家知道下 費事俾嚟啲人做壞個market啦<br />\n<br />\n大家得閒就去佢啲post度關心下佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c6e74c288f5982d8e42cd73ed341e9b114811e","tid":2203263,"uid":82631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:21:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid